  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个医疗诊断设备的状态流转图。核心设备是HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，它启动后先进入静止状态Still，然后需要和EMR系统同步数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Still",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以DiagnosticEngine触发后先到Still，Still再连到EMR_Sync。那Still之后还有什么状态吗？设备会开始移动或运行吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Still可以转换到Moving状态，表示设备开始运转采集数据。而且Moving和Still之间应该是双向的，设备可以暂停回到静止，也可以从静止恢复运行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上了Still到Moving的双向箭头。现在Moving还有一个出口需要处理吗？比如异常或终止的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Moving状态下可能发生Crash故障，这个Crash需要连接到HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，表示故障后转由实验室分析模块接手处理样本。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下结构：DiagnosticEngine启动→Still，Still分两支，一支去EMR_Sync同步，一支去Moving运行；Moving可以回Still，也可以进Crash；Crash最终到LabAnalyzer。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Still",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个流程。Crash到LabAnalyzer是单向的，故障移交后就不返回了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Crash",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了，用stateDiagram-v2画好了，标题设为Simple sample。所有状态流转都按你要求的医疗诊断场景配置好了。",
